<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A72FFECD2F40E58FDACFE2C" blockId="44.[173,946,1813,1861]" lastBlockId="45.[211,1444,301,699]" lastPageId="45" lastPageNumber="356" pageId="44" pageNumber="355">
Iconographie: 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A72FFEDD3610E58FE48F8C3" author="DIRSH V. M." box="[312,475,1841,1861]" pageId="44" pageNumber="355" refId="ref40777" refString="DIRSH V. M. 1965. - The African genera of Acridoidea. Cambridge University Press, 579 p." type="book" year="1965">Dirsh, 1965: 408</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A72FFEDD3B40E58FD08F8C3" author="MESTRE J." box="[493,667,1841,1861]" pageId="44" pageNumber="355" refId="ref42085" refString="MESTRE J. 1988. - Les Acridiens des formations herbeuses d'Afrique de l'Ouest. Ministere de la Cooperation, Paris; CIRAD-GERDAT-PRIFAS, Montpellier, 332 p." type="book" year="1988">Mestre, 1988: 181</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A72FFEDD0F70E58FC3DF8C3" author="LAMOTTE M. &amp; ROY R." box="[686,942,1841,1861]" pageId="44" pageNumber="355" pagination="81 - 132" refId="ref41949" refString="LAMOTTE M. &amp; ROY R. 1998. - La faune et le peuplement animal du Nimba, in LAMOTTE M. (ed.), Le mont Nimba, reserve de biosphere et site du patrimoine mondial (Guinee et Cote d'Ivoire): initiation a la geomorphologie et a la biogeographie. UNESCO Publishing: 81 - 132." type="book chapter" year="1998">Lamotte &amp; Roy, 1998: 107</bibRefCitation>
. Espèce de milieux herbacés, largement répartie en Afrique intertropicale. Déjà signalée du 
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A73FFECD6DF0844FB5FFEC2" box="[1158,1228,301,324]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Nimba</collectingRegion>
par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A73FFECD6A00844FE97FEE0" author="CHOPARD L." pageId="45" pageNumber="356" pagination="127 - 153" refId="ref40676" refString="CHOPARD L. 1958. - Acridiens, in La Reserve naturelle integrale du Mont Nimba, IV. Memoires de l'Institut francais d'Afrique noire 53: 127 - 153." type="journal article" year="1958">Chopard (1958: 146)</bibRefCitation>
sous le nom erroné de 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A73FFECD3AA0826FCFCFEE0" authority="I. Bolivar, 1908" authorityName="I. Bolivar" authorityYear="1908" box="[499,879,335,358]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Wilwerthia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acuminata">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD3AA0826FD5AFEE0" box="[499,713,335,358]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Wilwerthia acuminata</emphasis>
I. Bolivar, 1908
</taxonomicName>
(devenue depuis synonyme de 
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A73FFECD6EA0826FECAFE0E" authority="I. Bolivar, 1889" authorityName="I. Bolivar" authorityYear="1889" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Machaeridia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="conspersa">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD6EA0826FA1CFEE0" box="[1203,1423,335,358]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Machaeridia conspersa</emphasis>
I. Bolívar,1889
</taxonomicName>
, espèce d’Afrique centrale, orientale et australe), et par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A73FFECD1CD0818FBCBFE0E" author="DIRSH V. M." box="[916,1112,369,392]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" pagination="207 - 220" refId="ref40739" refString="DIRSH V. M. 1963. - Orthoptera Acridoidea (Second contribution), in La Reserve naturelle integrale du Mont Nimba, V. Memoires de l'Institut francais d'Afrique noire 66: 207 - 220." type="journal article" year="1963">Dirsh (1963: 216)</bibRefCitation>
, cette espèce y a fait l’objet d’un bon nombre de nouvelles captures.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C32845C11A73FFECD2AB08DFFBE5FBFE" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A73FFECD2AB08DFFE79FDF1" blockId="45.[211,1444,301,699]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A73FFECD2AB08DFFE87FE4B" box="[242,276,438,461]" country="Cameroon" name="East" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Les</collectingRegion>
milieux de capture sont essentiellement les savanes (Ziéla, Kéoulenta, Sérengbara, Gbakoré, plateau de Zouguépo 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD28A08B1FEC5FE69" box="[211,342,472,495]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.75" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="7.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="875.0" valueMax="1000.0" valueMin="750.0">750-1000 m</quantity>
, mont Zougué 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD3B508B1FDF1FE69" box="[492,610,472,495]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.75" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="7.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="775.0" valueMax="800.0" valueMin="750.0">750-800 m</quantity>
), les prairies sur cuirasse (près Gbakoré, près Gouéla, entre Bossou et Nion, plateau de Zouguépo 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD33A0893FE3AFD97" box="[355,425,506,529]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="750.0">750 m</quantity>
), les abords de marais (près Gbakoré), la prairie d’altitude (Pierré Richaud 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD6EF0893FAD5FD97" box="[1206,1350,506,529]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3" metricValueMax="1.6" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="1300.0" valueMax="1600.0" valueMin="1000.0">1000-1600 m</quantity>
, crête de Zouguépo 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD31B0B75FE07FDB5" box="[322,404,540,563]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="1200.0">1200 m</quantity>
, Grands Rochers 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD0110B75FD08FDB5" box="[584,667,540,563]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6199999999999999" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="1620.0">1620 m</quantity>
, signal Sempéré 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD11F0B75FC0BFDB5" box="[838,920,540,563]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.65" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="1650.0">1650 m</quantity>
), mais aussi à l’occasion les forêts-galeries (au bord du Zougué, 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD30B0B57FE5AFDD3" box="[338,457,574,597]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.25" metricValueMax="7.5" metricValueMin="7.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="m" value="725.0" valueMax="750.0" valueMin="700.0">700-750 m</quantity>
). Milieux non précisés pour Ziéla et Nion. 
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A73FFECD1D30B57FC3FFDD3" box="[906,940,574,597]" country="Cameroon" name="East" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Les</collectingRegion>
captures en altitude sont peu nombreuses, mais atteignent la ligne de crête.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A73FFECD2A80BEBFACEFD3D" blockId="45.[211,1444,301,699]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">
<collectingRegion id="49F6D8A81A73FFECD2A80BEBFE80FD1F" box="[241,275,642,665]" country="Cameroon" name="East" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Les</collectingRegion>
adultes sont présents de décembre à début avril. Des très jeunes ont été trouvés en juillet, des plus jeunes que l’avant-dernier stade en septembre, 1 jeune mâle au dernier stade et 1 jeune femelle à l’avant-dernier en octobre.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8D164A1A73FFECD3B30D25FBE5FBFE" blockId="45.[490,1167,1100,1144]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD3B30D25FDB9FBDB" bold="true" box="[490,554,1100,1117]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">FIG. 19.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A73FFECD0760D25FD6DFBDB" authority="Stal" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1873" box="[559,766,1100,1117]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Machaeridia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bilineata">
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD0760D25FD4BFBDB" box="[559,728,1100,1117]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Machaeridia bilineata</emphasis>
Stål
</taxonomicName>
, femelle, longueur 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD1CF0D25FC5CFBDB" box="[918,975,1100,1117]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="mm" value="35.0">35 mm</quantity>
; d’après 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A73FFECD6470D25FB18FBDB" author="MESTRE J." box="[1054,1163,1100,1117]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" refId="ref42085" refString="MESTRE J. 1988. - Les Acridiens des formations herbeuses d'Afrique de l'Ouest. Ministere de la Cooperation, Paris; CIRAD-GERDAT-PRIFAS, Montpellier, 332 p." type="book" year="1988">Mestre, 1988</bibRefCitation>
. 
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD05A0D0EFDD0FBFE" bold="true" box="[515,579,1127,1144]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">FIG. 19.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C326DC91A73FFECD0100D0EFC85FBFE" authority="Stal" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1873" box="[585,790,1127,1144]" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Machaeridia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bilineata">
Machaeridia bilineata 
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD0AE0D0EFC85FBFE" box="[759,790,1127,1144]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">Stål</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B946CA581A73FFECD14F0D0EFBE5FBFE" box="[790,1142,1127,1144]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="356">
, female, length 
<quantity id="4CCABBAF1A73FFECD1CE0D0EFC5CFBFE" box="[919,975,1127,1144]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" unit="mm" value="35.0">35 mm</quantity>
; after 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA36BBB1A73FFECD65C0D0EFBE1FBFE" author="MESTRE J." box="[1029,1138,1127,1144]" pageId="45" pageNumber="356" refId="ref42085" refString="MESTRE J. 1988. - Les Acridiens des formations herbeuses d'Afrique de l'Ouest. Ministere de la Cooperation, Paris; CIRAD-GERDAT-PRIFAS, Montpellier, 332 p." type="book" year="1988">Mestre, 1988</bibRefCitation>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
